Process called "shift_left" that takes value as String, shift_amount as Integer, value_type as String, options as Optional[BitwiseOptions] returns BitwiseResult:
    Note: Left bit shift operation (multiply by 2^shift_amount)
    Note: Shifts bits left, filling with zeros from right
    Note: Detects overflow when shifted bits are lost
    Note: Handles negative shift amounts as right shift
    
