Process called "shift_right" that takes value as String, shift_amount as Integer, value_type as String, options as Optional[BitwiseOptions] returns BitwiseResult:
    Note: Right bit shift operation (divide by 2^shift_amount)
    Note: Arithmetic shift for signed types (sign extension)
    Note: Logical shift for unsigned types (zero fill)
    Note: Handles negative shift amounts as left shift
    
