Process called "rotate_left" that takes value as String, rotation_amount as Integer, value_type as String returns BitwiseResult:
    Note: Left circular rotation (bits wrap around)
    Note: No bits are lost - they wrap from left to right
    Note: Rotation amount is modulo bit width
    Note: Useful for cryptographic and hashing operations
    
    Let result be BitwiseResult with:
        is_valid as false
        error_code as null
        error_message as null
        result_value as ""
        result_type as ""
        operation as "rotate_left"
