                Let digit_char be "8"
            Otherwise If remainder equals 9:
                Let digit_char be "9"
            
            Let digit_stack be digit_char concatenated with digit_stack
            Let temp_value be temp_value divided by 10
        
        Let result.result_value be digit_stack
    
    Note: Set result metadata
    Let result.result_type be "uint" concatenated with bit_count
    Let result.bit_width be bit_count
    Let result.signed_result be false
    Let result.is_valid be true
    Let result.operations_performed be 1
    Return result

Process called "insert_bit_field" that takes target as String, field_value as String, start_bit as Integer, bit_count as Integer, target_type as String returns BitwiseResult:
    Note: Insert bit field into target value at specified position
