Process called "gray_code_encode" that takes value as String, value_type as String returns BitwiseResult:
    Note: Convert binary value to Gray code
    Note: Gray code changes only one bit between consecutive values
    Note: Useful for error detection and correction
    
    Let result be BitwiseResult with:
        is_valid as false
        error_code as null
        error_message as null
        result_value as ""
        result_type as ""
