    Let result.bit_width be bit_width
    Let result.is_valid be true
    Let result.operations_performed be 1
    Return result

Process called "gray_code_decode" that takes gray_value as String, value_type as String returns BitwiseResult:
    Note: Convert Gray code back to binary
    Note: Inverse operation of Gray code encoding
